OL,3,CStorm Ciaran: One year on and how it's
OL,4,Cstill affecting people in Jersey
OL,6,FIt will be a year tomorrow since Storm
OL,7,FCiaran swept through the Channel
OL,8,FIslands and some people are still
OL,9,Ffeeling the effects.
OL,11,FHurricane-force winds and the most
OL,12,Fpowerful tornado ever recorded in
OL,13,FJersey caused destruction on an
OL,14,Funprecedented scale.
OL,16,FOne islander who's home was damaged
OL,17,Fsays the experience altered her
OL,18,Fperspective on life.
