OL,3,CStorm Ciaran: One year on and how it's
OL,4,Cstill affecting people in Jersey
OL,6,FRachel O'Brien said: "I actually took
OL,7,Fa year off work which I hadn't planned
OL,8,Fon doing. I needed time and wanted to
OL,9,Fbe around the kids a bit as well to
OL,10,Flook after them, they're grown up but
OL,11,Fwe wanted to be together.
OL,13,F"I think it was good because I don't
OL,14,Freally like change and this was a big
OL,15,Fchange, but it's made me incredibly
OL,16,Fgrateful. We should have been dead
OL,17,Fthat night."
OL,19,FHundreds of homes were damaged in the
OL,20,Fstorm and for some, the repair work is
OL,21,Fyet to be completed.
