OL,3,CStorm Ciaran: One year on and how it's
OL,4,Cstill affecting people in Jersey
OL,6,FThe demand for contractors continues
OL,7,Fto outweigh the supply, with many
OL,8,Fresidents still in temporary
OL,9,Faccommodation.
OL,11,FFliquet in St Martin was also severely
OL,12,Faffected. What was a vibrant Jersey
OL,13,Fcommunity is now derelict and the
OL,14,Fhomes are boarded up.
OL,16,FTony Perchard is lucky to be alive
OL,17,Fafter he was sucked out of his bed
OL,18,Fless than a second before debris
OL,19,Flanded exactly where he had been lying.
