OL,3,CStorm Ciaran: One year on and how it's
OL,4,Cstill affecting people in Jersey
OL,6,FHe says: "It's going to take a while
OL,7,Feven longer to come to terms with it
OL,8,Fall because we've no longer got a
OL,9,Fhouse, the house is a shell, we lost
OL,10,Feverything, clothes, the lot.
OL,12,FHis wife, Evie, added: "Things that
OL,13,Fyou've accumulated that you thought
OL,14,Fwere really important aren't and the
OL,15,Fone thing that has struck me is to
OL,16,Fappreciate people as we have had such
OL,17,Fkindness and generosity that it really
OL,18,Fmakes you think, 'well, there's got to
OL,19,Fbe something rather than living for
OL,20,Fwhat you can get'."
